Added WireCard (http://www.wirecard.com) Gateway.

Supports:
* authorize
* capture
* purchase
* recurring (uses authorization as initial request and a purchase as repeated request)

Unit and Remote Tests provided.

TODO:
* provide credit card owner names with credit card details
* allow further settings in the XML messages

WireCard requires a fixed IP address for production system.

GitHub SourceCode: http://github.com/SachaSchlegel/active_merchant/tree/master

